- **CLI Commands**:
  - `git clone https://github.com/tiangolo/fastapi-sqlalchemy.git`
  - `pip install fastapi sqlalchemy alembic`

- **Latest Versions**:
  - FastAPI: v0.95.1
  - SQLAlchemy: v1.4.32
  - Alembic: v1.7.6

- **Key Config Options**:
  - Database URL: `SQLALCHEMY_DATABASE_URL = "postgresql+asyncpg://user:password@localhost/dbname"`
  - Tortoise ORM: `TORTOISE_ORM = {
      'connections': {'default': 'sqlite:///db.sqlite3'},
      'apps': {
          'models': {
              'models': ['__main__'],
              'default_connection': 'default',
          },
      },
  }`
